articles.title: Ukraine carries out armed raid in Crimea, inflicts casualties on Russia - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Covert forces hit Russian troops and gear during daring military operation, Kyiv says.
articles.content:
KYIV Ukraine on Thursday conducted a daring operation in Russian-occupied Crimea, its military intelligence said, as Kyiv marked the anniversary of independence from the Soviet Union in 1991.
